{"tid":710804,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《阿甘正傳》導演新作 模型撚以FF克服心理創傷","createTime":"2018-06-21T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T05:04:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92f5d3a943ced5501e89489587d1f5a58ae41f75","tid":710804,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Li2dHr5Q-JY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLi2dHr5Q-JY&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291Mzfl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=64a652ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Li2dHr5Q-JY</a><br />\n<br />\n故事敘述在酒吧外遭五名男子襲擊的馬克，一度命危昏迷九天。出院後的他，認識了新朋友，更在自家後院打造了1/6尺寸的二戰時期比利時小鎮模型，並稱之為馬文鎮，馬克透過製作模型漸漸克服他的心理創傷。北美預計今年11月21日上映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/130046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F130046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=33c1a189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b368d30e35bd173a3635a951642a6ccee2d1f3d","tid":710804,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"笑鳩人唔識Robert Zemeckis"},{"pid":"cbdcde9bfa7a82679fefa96a7bfc7eb4bf5ec2d0","tid":710804,"uid":47719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}